GeoIP             x.x                                  Yes              GeoIP Maxmind conversion
JCrop			  0.9.8	   MIT Licence				   Yes				JS library to crop images
JQuery            1.4.4    GPL and MIT Licence         Yes              JS library,Layout,TableDND
